<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(ت)</span> , وَعَنْ أَنَسِ بْنَ مَالِكٍ - رضي الله عنه -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> إِنْ لَمْ نَكُنْ مِنْ الْأَزْدِ , فَلَسْنَا مِنْ النَّاسِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>. <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
